Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.49,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.78,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,waves makes me feel a bit tingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:23.32,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:58.93,Episode-Title - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(526,521)}Episode 7\N "Bicycle"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.14,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.41,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:07.30,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.59,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You've liked girls before, too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of it as anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,more than a weird feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:28.01,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you'd like such a simple girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.89,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.51,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.26,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully you won't need us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:41.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.25,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,All I can hear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.74,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,is your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:04.54,Flashback,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I keep seeing you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.14,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, Yana-chan is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.54,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.98,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? So what's the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.45,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-meter freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.87,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I just hit 32 seconds the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.01,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is 31 seconds flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.17,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going for it, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.00,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're working toward your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.29,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,dream job as a model, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.89,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I've secretly been rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.45,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do have a nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.98,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.86,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.13,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go shopping for clothes sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.23,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.21,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You would? Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.32,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for just showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.45,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.89,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:53.96,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.96,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,About Yuki-kun the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That slap of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:11.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I didn't like \Nwhat Kakeru-kun did either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.98,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. You make yourself so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.84,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.59,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.10,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.37,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't he tell he doesn't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear Sachi is staying \Nat the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.21,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.53,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about then, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:43.52,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We should hold back on the visits, \Nso we don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.64,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,let's not get in the way \Nof their secret dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan's fine. It looks \Nlike she's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:03.73,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.39,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I think she'd be happy if we visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.46,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so scattered lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a bit weird, ever\N since that David showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.04,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Visiting hours at the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,end so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd let us stay till 10 PM at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.27,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your pianist hands are so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.16,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes a crescendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.04,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.39,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fortissimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.77,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.71,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.76,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if there's anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.45,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.50,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend, Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.90,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.67,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.53,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sachi's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sacchan's b-b-boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro Shirosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa made these cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.59,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was \Na swallow's nest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hatchlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.51,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are at least two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've lived here all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but you seem to know so \Nmuch more about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me a little unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.07,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing a few small things about this city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:53.36,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't compare to you having lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.13,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.07,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.61,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan came over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are we,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:20.93,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,you and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Have we become more than
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,just two people who share a weird ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.84,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay as long as \Nwe stay like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,The future can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.10,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The beach tomorrow. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.35,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.40,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:17.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.90,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,There he is, right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.99,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming, the 5:30 guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.37,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.18,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sister's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.12,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.33,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You know him? Have you talked to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.18,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.54,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.30,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's just so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.23,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.32,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard he's kind of in a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.30,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.53,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.08,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.34,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,You've been training, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.80,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Your record at the track \Nmeet—I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.76,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.43,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.01,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if you want to talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.41,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have summer camp for a week \Nstarting the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.56,Main,Coach,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer if you could call \Nme before or after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.51,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard first thing in \Nthe morning, huh, Onee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:06.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're keeping up well \Nwith your club work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.52,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.88,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Yukinari-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:15.27,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,From our pool we can\Nsee him on his routine run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.09,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.43,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,but he's kind of our club's idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.63,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about making \Na fan club and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's Yuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.66,Main,Huh,0000,0000,0000,,Small world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-kun's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.02,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,True, he looked good running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.14,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Yuki-kun is good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.51,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.85,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a bad liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:53.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm going to go visit Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.18,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.96,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,My tests are starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.12,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.24,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:13.79,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.23,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.67,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,How are you? Doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.94,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.87,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A gift from Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.33,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.34,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, Okikura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.76,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.01,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So Kakeru-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,said something a bit nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan heard him, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.04,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.30,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I heard the weather \Nwill be nice tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe if we went to \Nthe beach together tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.78,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.61,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe I might see something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:31.04,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,"Something"? Those sparkly things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think being with Kakeru-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.00,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to understand what those are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know when I have a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.60,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.51,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:03.74,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.87,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The coach is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:05.53,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.22,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hi again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:20.38,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Touko Fukami's sister, Hina Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.75,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.26,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,please stay attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.63,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.64,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sacchan? It's so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.78,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.83,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being discharged tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.79,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.43,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Yukinari-kun \Nand Yanagi-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.24,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to light fireworks at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.21,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.94,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's short notice, \Nbut I'll let Touko-chan know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:43.90,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.69,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Yanagi-san and Yukinari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.28,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You never replied to my message \Nabout going to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can make it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi-san said she can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.11,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "ah" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:16.70,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:27.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to the beach with his \Ngirlfriend today, right? How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.84,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He's grown up to be a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.61,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I think he's a charming young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.14,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like \Nsomething a mother would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.85,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that thing—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.83,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The tests got delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.84,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's staying until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.48,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi, I'm positive I told you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:51.93,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.15,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.06,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're causing trouble for Mr. Boyfriend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,No, what trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Mr. Boyfriend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.16,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.59,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.88,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.79,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:11.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.01,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Sachi, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:14.79,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I should text everyone to let \Nthem know we're canceling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.38,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I hate David.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You do? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.73,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets split up when he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:36.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,True, everyone's kind of scattered lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:40.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so should we move the beach to tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.46,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-chan has a date at \NHinode Beach with David.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.97,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,So I never contacted Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:50.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,you tried to get everyone to ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,David's date with Touko, \Njust because you hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:17:59.96,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.37,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So you called me to get me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.11,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.31,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.26,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.22,Sign - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.29,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.23,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing the beach trip today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.70,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.25,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing the beach trip today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.26,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.18,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So you did wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it tingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.14,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It feels a bit different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:33.31,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that I've ever \Ncome at this time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.61,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.09,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Glass beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.37,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You said I would fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I did. Don't ever go anywhere high!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:55.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,To put it bluntly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.12,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I can never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.16,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,go anywhere I might fall from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.73,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Then what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really fragments of the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one that told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.14,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We should think it over a bit more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.96,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go buy juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.71,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:26.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,As a kid, I used to wonder why grown-ups pay
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:30.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,money to buy water and tea \Nfrom vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.67,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There's Halpis Water right next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.10,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were invited, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.31,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Touko with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She went to get something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:59.69,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Now's a good time to tell you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.65,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault Yuki \Nisn't attractive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.54,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.83,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:14.96,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.88,Flashback,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a cute couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:25.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:30.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:31.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:32.90,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get a proper explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.30,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I won't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.80,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, what's wrong? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:39.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to visit Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.06,Episode-Title - End,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8\N"Snow"
